From cou.: 6 Direct experimental determination of the structures of larger MgO clusters has been carried out by Kim et al., using transmission electron microscopy.9 Their experiments showed that cube-like nanoparticles, of edge length 2–3 nm (containing about 1000 ions) adopt the rocksalt structure.
From Soup: 6 Direct experimental determination of the structures of larger MgO clusters has been carried out by Kim et al ., using transmission electron microscopy . 9 Their experiments showed that cube-like nanoparticles , of edge length 2–3 nm (containing about 1000 ions) adopt the rocksalt structure.
