From cou.: 7 Many theoretical studies have been carried out on neutral and charged MgO clusters, using a variety of theoretical approaches,7,8,10–21 and most of these studies will be described in the Results and discussion section.
From Soup: 7 Many theoretical studies have been carried out on neutral and charged MgO clusters, using a variety of theoretical approaches, 7,8,10–21 and most of these studies will be described in the Results and discussion section.
